<br>
Right now, I presume you're not post 60, and you aren't raiding the higher tier planes.  Getting runspeed, innate regeneration, mental clarity, SCM, SCF, etc, are all much more important and will make a difference in your efficiency as a cleric.  If you really really want that wisdom, you could always do it later, once you have the more important AAs.  5 AA points are much better spent in plenty of different areas.<br>
